column5: Hi all,  Just like to show off what i got for christmas. I got a okuma sheffield man what a sweet reel. so smooth. I am practicing like crazy man i can already wallis cast all i need to do is to get to a river that has some steelhead and iam all set.   Okuma Sheffield       jordan
